\f0\fs24 \cf0 # Sojern Design System\
\
A React component library built from the Sojern Figma design system.\
\
## Components included\
Button, Chip, Toast, Toggle, Checkbox, Radio, Breadcrumb, Tabs,\
Tooltip, FormInput, Modal, Sidebar, Table, Pagination, Card,\
Stepper, PageLayout\
\
## How to use with Cursor\
1. Open this folder in Cursor\
2. Cursor automatically reads CLAUDE.md for design system rules\
3. Ask Cursor to build pages using the existing components\
\
## Example prompts\
- "Build a campaigns list page with sidebar, table and pagination"\
- "Create a create campaign wizard with a 4 step stepper"\
- "Build a reporting dashboard with metric cards and a data table"\
\
